reviewtext: Excellent product! Packs good lows and mids with pretty good bass. For the last 6 years, I was using Sony MDR710, excellent portable headphones. I ordered Sennheiser PX200 II recently but found it greatly lacked the bass! Returned it and ordered these seeing the great reviews. It's just a few notches down as compared to Sony MDR710/Sennheiser PX 200II. But has good bass as compared to PX 200, which cost ten times more!
summary: Excellent! Good lows, mids and bass
